# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. Excludes installed
# deps and build outputs so `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` runs clean.
# NOTE: this only affects image builds; the solana service mounts
# contracts-sol/target/deploy/*.so as a volume, which .dockerignore does not affect.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.turbo
website/test-results
website/playwright-report
website/storybook-static

# Rust / Anchor build artifacts (large, not needed for the web build).
# Match every Cargo/Anchor target dir anywhere in the tree — the Rust SDK
# (sdk/rust/target) alone is tens of GB and was previously shipped to the
# daemon on every build, dominating the build-context transfer.
**/target
contracts-sol/target
fuzz/target

.git
.github
*.log
.DS_Store
